00095 template<unsigned DIM>
00096 MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw<DIM>::MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw(double c1, double c2)
00097     : mC1(c1),
00098       mC2(c2)
00099 {
00100     assert(DIM==2 || DIM ==3);
00101 
00102     // If dim==3, check that c2 was passed in, ie c2 isn't the default value
00103     if ((DIM==3) && (c2<MINUS_LARGE+1))
00104     {
00105         EXCEPTION("Two parameters needed for 3d Mooney-Rivlin");
00106     }
00107 
00108     if (c1 < 0.0)
00109     {
00110         EXCEPTION("c1 must be positive in mooney-rivlin"); // is this correct?
00111     }
00112 }
